OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChild killer jailed for 29 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fyears over 1992 murder     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A child killer who murdered a          
OL,6, seven-year-old girl in 1992 has been   
OL,7, jailed for at least 29 years.          
OL,9,FDavid Boyd, 55, lured Nikki Allan to a 
OL,10,Fderelict building in Sunderland where  
OL,11,Fhe beat her and stabbed her 37 times.  
OL,13,FJudge Mrs Justice Lambert said Nikki   
OL,14,Fmust have endured "unimaginable fear"  
OL,15,Fin the moments before her death.       
OL,17,FBoyd, who was eventually snared by DNA 
OL,18,Fadvances in 2017, was sentenced to life
OL,19,Fafter being convicted of murder earlier
OL,20,Fthis month at Newcastle Crown Court.   
